{"tid":346213,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"（招人）識寫app或者讀過遊戲美術設計的你入一入黎","createTime":"2017-08-03T18:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T04:27:46.000Z","uid":133126,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc41bf350193debaa16a2fb945d10e7d5916dce3","tid":346213,"uid":133126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T18:09:59.000Z","msg":"小弟黎緊會參加一個ACG青年創業比賽，以開發一個手機線上遊戲為參賽作品。現需：<br />\n<br />\n1. 遊戲程式開發員<br />\n2. 遊戲原畫師<br />\n<br />\n另外符合以下條件優先考慮：<br />\n18歲-35歲（大會要求）<br />\n對港澳台地區手機線上遊戲市場有一定了解<br />\n熟悉手機遊戲公司一般運作<br />\n<br />\n分紅方面：3：3：3：1（程式開發員：遊戲原畫師：企業策劃：本人）<br />\n<br />\n詳細d黎講，假設我地個團體獲得獎金10萬，遊戲程式開發員、遊戲原畫師同企業策劃均會獲得三成獎金即3萬港元為酬，而本人則獲一成。<br />\n<br />\n有意請tg到時再講details<br />\n<br />\ntg：iamterrytoogood"},{"pid":"a8faa5ff8a7007a68e899c5a2eca24cd93c205b3","tid":346213,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T23:10:48.000Z","msg":"你負責報名就拎一成？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a1c36b999886d07feac11261c1da2ae82de87f","tid":346213,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T23:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你負責報名就拎一成？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主負責組織 <br />\n你估易做 <br />\n你有本事你唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34305e90b23a96d8e97134faf0570d044117bbc9","tid":346213,"uid":133126,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:42:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你負責報名就拎一成？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔系，我負責遊戲劇本編寫，遊戲角色人格設定，世界觀建構等等。"},{"pid":"e305acb66320b6e6d8f6cba25b6ad30ec1291fc7","tid":346213,"uid":133126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:44:00.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"089c9421af484556b77e327cc91e89cc3f8bcd07","tid":346213,"uid":26242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:50:04